♪ Oh oh

35:37.969 --> 35:40.170
You okay?

35:41.372 --> 35:42.939
I don't know
what I feel.

35:42.941 --> 35:46.977
Listen, I'm really sorry
about the way the night went.

35:46.979 --> 35:49.579
I know that I promised you
that I wouldn't be a cop,

35:49.581 --> 35:51.281
track your car
or follow you.

35:51.283 --> 35:54.117
But, I knew that you
were going to meet Crash,

35:54.119 --> 35:56.520
and I couldn't
let that happen.

35:56.522 --> 35:59.523
I knew that.

35:59.525 --> 36:00.957
What?

36:00.959 --> 36:05.095
I knew you were gonna
follow me.

36:05.097 --> 36:06.396
In fact, I was
counting on it.

36:06.398 --> 36:10.167
I don't understand
what you're telling me.

36:13.337 --> 36:15.005
Look...

36:15.007 --> 36:18.241
when Crash told me he
was gonna leave town,

36:18.243 --> 36:21.211
a big part of me just
wanted to let him go

36:21.213 --> 36:26.550
and-- and just let
the whole thing be over.

36:26.552 --> 36:30.086
But, I could never
do that to Max.

36:30.922 --> 36:33.156
Why didn't you say
something to me?

36:33.158 --> 36:35.458
Because, I needed
to see him.

36:35.460 --> 36:37.594
I needed to hear
what he had to say.

36:37.596 --> 36:40.931
I really don't think
anyone does anything

36:40.933 --> 36:43.867
for no reason
whatsoever.

36:43.869 --> 36:46.636
You taught me that,
actually.

36:46.638 --> 36:49.573
I really thought
I could convince him

36:49.575 --> 36:51.408
to hand himself in.

36:51.410 --> 36:54.511
But... I was scared.

36:54.513 --> 36:59.115
I didn't know if he
still had the gun and...

36:59.117 --> 37:02.285
I didn't wanna
do it alone.

37:02.287 --> 37:04.087
But I knew
I wouldn't have to.

37:04.089 --> 37:06.523
You wanted me
to be there.

37:07.658 --> 37:10.393
I needed you
to protect me.

37:12.296 --> 37:13.930
(sighing)

37:13.932 --> 37:16.533
'Cause you're my mom.

37:20.004 --> 37:22.706
And I love you.

37:27.211 --> 37:29.446
I love you.

37:29.448 --> 37:38.221
♪

37:42.693 --> 37:44.327
(sighing)

37:46.097 --> 37:47.497
Hey.

37:47.499 --> 37:50.033
Hey.

37:50.968 --> 37:52.535
Is anyone in there?

37:52.537 --> 37:54.971
I was, but I had
to leave.

37:54.973 --> 37:57.240
I couldn't take
the beeping anymore.

37:58.342 --> 38:00.043
Dad took Karen
to a hotel.

38:00.045 --> 38:01.278
You can go in
if you want.

38:01.280 --> 38:04.581
Can we talk for
a second first?

38:04.583 --> 38:07.284
Sure.

38:08.219 --> 38:10.453
Please don't
give up on me.

38:10.455 --> 38:13.657
I've put you through hell.

38:13.659 --> 38:16.893
I'm still putting
you through hell.

38:16.895 --> 38:18.295
But, I promise you,

38:18.297 --> 38:21.298
I'm going to
make it up to you.

38:24.001 --> 38:27.404
Thanks for having
Crash arrested.

38:29.440 --> 38:32.309
Was that hard?

38:32.311 --> 38:35.512
(sighs)

38:35.514 --> 38:38.014
I loved him.

38:40.184 --> 38:45.955
And for whatever reason,
I couldn't see past that.

38:45.957 --> 38:47.991
Sorry.

38:47.993 --> 38:51.528
Do you still
love him?

38:58.169 --> 38:59.035
Thank you.

38:59.037 --> 39:00.670
Mom said you were
really great.

39:00.672 --> 39:06.009
She says you have a future
in hostage negotiating.

39:07.078 --> 39:09.979
Great.
Thanks, Mom.

39:10.181 --> 39:13.917
That's the first time I've
heard you make that mistake.

39:13.919 --> 39:15.885
(laughing)
Oh.

39:15.887 --> 39:19.255
Um, not a mistake.

39:19.257 --> 39:21.458
Wow.

39:21.460 --> 39:22.625
That's big.

39:22.627 --> 39:25.061
Yeah.

39:25.063 --> 39:27.230
Wanna go in?

39:29.367 --> 39:36.439
♪

39:36.441 --> 39:41.111
(monitors beeping)

39:41.113 --> 39:45.582
Doctor says he could
make a full recovery.

39:45.584 --> 39:49.386
So we shouldn't
give up hope.

39:50.454 --> 39:54.457
Well, I'm not
giving up hope.

39:54.459 --> 39:55.525
Are you?

39:55.527 --> 39:59.329
Hell, no.
Never.

40:00.965 --> 40:03.299
Oh, I brought you
some stuff.

40:03.301 --> 40:07.070
Clothes and stuff, so you've
got something to wear.

40:08.472 --> 40:10.907
Carter, this is
your sweater.

40:10.909 --> 40:12.108
Oh, yeah, I know.

40:12.110 --> 40:13.510
But you always said
how much you liked it.

40:13.512 --> 40:16.679
And your makeup bag's
in there as well.

40:17.948 --> 40:20.483
You know...

40:20.485 --> 40:22.118
when Max wakes up.

